sections.text: Raghavender Manai Founder, CEO, Data Science Analytics Senior Manager LearnInbox.com, WriteBox.co 9866005283 RisingRoot Technologies Pvt Ltd raghav@learninbox.com

Strategic Planning & Management • Business Development • Multi-Site Business Operations • Product & Service Management• Competition & Market Analysis • Channel Management • Client Satisfaction • Training & Development • Ed Tech • General Mgt • Media-Tech • E-commerce • Trainer • R&D manager • Developer

Professional Summary I am having more than 17years of experience, during the professional journey I have been in multiple roles, I was a solution architect, business development manager, product analyst, market analyst, brand manager, researcher, developer, trainer, and mentor. I dealt with multiple projects and training I was being associated with various Business partners to explore the business and marketing opportunities I was a founder for few software firms in mid-of my professional journey. Customer-focused visionary and respected industry leader known for leading global teams to build revolutionary digital solutions. Experience in Global Program Delivery Management, Project Management, Enterprise Architecture, and leading all agile project phases including (Discover, Prepare, Explore, Realize, Deploy and Run). Managed roadmap to adopt and deploy new technology components with API and microservices that tie to business needs, working closely with IT teams to achieve this. Experience in Intelligent Enterprise Services (Customer Experience, People Engagement, Digital Core, Manufacturing & Supply Chain, Network & Spend Management), Automation Services, Digital Assurance Services, and Intelligent Enterprise Applications using Robotics Process Automation (RPA), Artificial Intelligence (RPA). Experience in Digital Content, Digital Engagement, Customer Engagement & E-commerce Solutions, helped to address organizational, business process, and technology ecosystems to achieve goals, designed digital marketing strategies to drive greater synergy.

Area of Expertise ➢ Establishing short/long term budgets in tune with corporate strategies for achieving business targets. ➢ Expertise and Hands-on experience in open source Solution Enterprise Java stack, Python, PHP, Perl, Angular, JavaScript frameworks, Data Science, Analytics Solutions, Bigdata Management, Andriod, and iOS app Development. ➢ Formulating business planning, forecasting & analysis for assessment of revenue potential in business opportunities. ➢ Developing relationships with key decision-makers in target organizations and establishing tie-ups for business development.

➢ Analyzing & reviewing the market response/requirements and communicating the same to the sales teams for the accomplishment of the business goals. ➢ Overseeing the sales & marketing operations, thereby achieving increased business growth. ➢ Identifying streams for generating revenues & developing marketing plans to build consumer preference. ➢ Conducting competitor analysis by keeping abreast of market trends & achieving market share metrics. ➢ Recruiting, leading, mentoring & monitoring the team members to ensure efficiency in process operations and meeting of individual & group targets. ➢ Extensive experience in promoting and developing executive education programs (EEPs), management development programs (MDPs), faculty development programs (FDPs), learning courses series (blended & hybrid), besides immersive & certification courses for working executives, professionals, faculty, and corporates ➢ Certified professional in project management, education psychology, AWS services & Ed-cloud solutions with proven ability to create and drive ambition incorporates, govt., enterprises, and academic institution Key Results Business Development & Market Growth: Developing and executing the company's business development roadmap, creating new funnels, and growing revenue, while ensuring alignment with our long-term vision, mission, and strategy. Identifying, analyzing, and developing new business opportunities and ensuring partnerships are executed successfully from start to finish; from signing agreements, onboarding new partners, and driving business. Business Strategic Partnerships: Fostering the growth of the company's existing business units (or drive the creation of a new BU) via formulation of strategies, strategic partnerships, product/solution development plans. Establishing and growing a differentiated, high-value business in new markets. Providing business & market intelligence briefings and recommendations to the senior executive staff. Customer Relationship Management: Maintaining cordial relations with customers to sustain the profitability of the business. Maximize customer satisfaction level by on time delivery, monitoring customer complaints, providing efficient services. Handling customer grievances and resolving issues. Excellent client relationship management, time & resource management. Team Management: Innovative and results-driven senior manager focused on achieving exceptional results in highly competitive environments that demand continuous improvement. Expertise in building and motivating large teams that well exceed corporate expectations.
Leadership: Advises the management on business strategies promotes organization among customers & vendors and drives organization mission through employees & supports motivation of employees

Professional Key Highlights ➢ More than 150+ employees were worked under my mentorship ➢ 10000+ Students were undergone professional and academic training during my professional experience ➢ 200+ Ph.D. Scholars completed their Ph.D.'s and more than 3000+ masters students finished their post-graduation ➢ 300+ Research papers were supported on behalf of research scholars. I have written papers on security, big data, communication, and blockchain domains ➢ 250+ Vendors are enrolled as a service provider in LearnInbox and Writebox ➢ More than 20+ client projects handled in Health care, e-media, and e commerce, etc ➢ Conducted more than 25+ workshops on various universities ➢ Worked more than 15 years in B2B and B2C sector
Products and Tools Experience Product Details Role Virtual Requirement Assistance with AI Product Manager, UI/UX, and DB Architect Virtual DashBoards Architect and Product Manager

Virtual Support Desk Solution Architect and Delivery Manager Referral and Earn Lead Generation Product Manager and Business Head Virtual Q&A model Generation (QAI System) AI Delivery Engineer Virtual Performace Indicator Data scientist Delivery Head AI-Powered Smart Skill Assessment Tool Architect and AI Solution Manager Virtual Dashboard Bots Product Manager and Delivery Head Payout Generation Sr Business Analyst and Product Manager Push Notification Tool Delivery Manager and Product Engineer

Skill-Set Simulators: NS2, NS3, OMNET++, OPNET, Cisco packet Tracer, Cooja Languages: C, C++, Python, JAVA, TCL, OTCL Protocols: TCP/IP, OSPF, UDP, BGP, etc Frameworks: Laravel, Magento Tools: Agile, Scrum master, JIRA Cloud Servers: AWS, Microsoft Azure, Docker, and GCS UI/UX Technologies: ReactJS, NodeJS and AngularJS, JavaScript,CSS, Bootstrap, HTML5 Operating System: Windows, and Ubuntu Specialized areas: Big data, Data mining, AI, ML, Networking, Network Security, Image processing Key Skills: Business Analysis, Business Process Management, Requirement Analysis, Project Management, Business Intelligence, Business Development, Business Strategy, Business planning, Go to market strategy, project planning, CRM

Professional Experience RisingRoot Technologies Pvt Ltd: CEO (July 2019 – Till Date) Experienced Technical Director with a demonstrated history of working in theB2B and B2C industries. Versatile senior technology executive with a proven track record

building business, satisfying customers, and delivering flawless execution. Deep experience with Programmatic Marketing, Conversational AI, Cloud, Data Science, and other new technologies. Talented at building high-performance teams working in a high-dynamic, multi-cultural, and geographically dispersed environment Strategic Alliances: Formation of Privilege Card Business Model for the long term business with retail customers New Product Development: Coming up with a new product line for the company to increase the business volume OPERATIONS - Digital Transformation, Business Networking, People Management, Lean Service Operations, Customer support/service, Organizational Building, and Organizational Development

LearnInbox: (https://learninbox.com) Founder (July 2019 – Till Date) After a deep understanding of the market and business opportunities, I framed the idea of learninbox, The learn inbox was initially started with 4 people and made a lot of research to understand the process and explore the business solution. At an early stage, the conversion of ideas into the process took me near about one 1year, during this journey I gained good experience and exposure in the open market. I have paid a lot of attention to develop dashboards and brought customized price orders. The LearnInbox platform is made with 360-degree e-learning solutions for kids to adults. Designing of product architecture and understanding of business needs Exploring of various business and marketing opportunities to frame the go-to marketing Enhance the market opportunity by exploring the various products and engaged the various vendors to be part of LearnInbox Largely Responsible for Research, Ideation, Team building, Strategy, Design, Growth, Funding & more. Designed a full-stack Business model Identified various Revenue streams Designed & Lead Marketing, Sales & Customer Acquisition campaigns Key Role in Product Design, Development & Research: 1. Consumer features 2. UI/UX 3. Latest Technology Integration (ML/AI) 4. Track of Usage & Supply 5. Data Analysis 6. Back-end Innovation 7. Content Management 8. Product Flow Layout

WriteBox: (https://writebox.co) Founder (June 2021 – Till Date) WriteBox is an open marketplace for professional and academic writing services. The platform was built to assist Ph.D. Research scholars, Master's students, and Graduate students on different subjects. The platform is integrated with a price calculator, for easy payment estimation and generation. WriteBox have more than 200+ Writers to offer different Writing services 1) Branding Strategies 2) Resource Building 3) Project Management Strategies 4) Case Studies and Research on Digital Best Practices 5) Digital Analytics Vertex Soft: Founder (July 2009 – Till Date) Vertex Soft is an e-learning platform that provides research and development opportunities for research scholars It's a different spell in my journey I was contributed to various research activities in networking, communication, security, data mining, image mining, and cloud computing I worked with various research scholars and developed various simulation models in communication and security domains Written various research papers and my written paper were published in reputed journals I have a vast experience in NS2, NS3, Python, OMNET, OPNET, Cloudsim, Packetsim, C, C++, and JAVA Conducted various workshops on simulations tools and trained 10000+ students across the world VLS Solutions Pvt Ltd ➢ I was the founder for this organization, I founded this organization in 2011 with small java and dot net team ➢ I worked with online media portals and developed online newspaper suryaa news ➢ I worked as a product analyst and architecture and developed a customized media portal ➢ During this period, we developed more than 18 projects in health care, industrial services, and media portals ➢ I designed and developed a job portal i.e jobmirchi.com in PHP and WordPress. At the early stage of the product, I have explored business opportunities with various vendors.

➢ The jobmirchi.com portal was a customized platform where vendors were easily managed their hiring activities CJ Soft Pvt Ltd: Manager-(Jan 2007 – June 2009) ➢ CJ soft was a start-up and dealt with web development products. I worked as a project manager and connected with the open market for enriching the marketing opportunities in the logistic and online order management platforms ➢ Developed online order management prototype for food order systems, and e-transport. ➢ Explored the market opportunities by integrating feasible and customized solutions for restaurants ➢ Integrated the B2B and B2C lead automation system, for lead acquisition Sysmec Technologies India Pvt Ltd: Software Engineer (July 2006- Dec 2007) ➢ After one and a half years of my journey with Ensparc, I stepped into Sysmec Technologies as a Java developer. Sysmec technologies developed automation products, it's the first company that started Local Ticketing system and Salary Dispenser system in India. ➢ I was well known as a product analyst; I designed a communication protocol to interconnect a gateway server to the local machine ➢ Designed a GSP communication prototype to perform ticket dispensing, and cost management ➢ Developed a native application for language assistance Ensparc Solutions Pvt Ltd: Software Engineer (Feb 2004- June 2006) My journey started in the year 2004, when I was in graduation, we started a digital magazine to brough freeware and shareware software's, tools and e-tutorials. At an early stage, we explored our direct marketing opportunities in top cities across India.
Qualification B.Tech, CSE from Jawaharlal Nehru Technological University Hyderabad in 2005
